{
  "stem": "11144.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother was avoiding it by giving all kinds of excuses, really.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She's not-- da, da, da, da, da, until it got to a point where he finally kicked us out from there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because he couldn't get it, he kicked us out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And where did you go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- before we end this, I don't remember whether that was in this particular place, where I developed rheumatic fever.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My uncle got typhoid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, later on, my mother got typhoid.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, thank God both of them survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The typhoid, I guess, was not that severe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, I with that-- with my rheumatic fever, I was sick for about half a year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I walked out, outside, because there was-- as I said, there was no plumbing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went outside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I had to release myself, or I fell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I couldn't get up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "For half a year, I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I couldn't-- I was incapacitated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't do anything with my hands and I couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I stayed in bed for about half a year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, I think we were in this guy's house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But what had happened, that at that time, my mother had developed somehow-- there was a priest, with whom my parents-- my mother, not my-- my father was not alive anymore.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother developed, you know, some kind of a relationship because she started begging, I think.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When she was begging, she went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She knocked at this priest's house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--the housekeeper was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was giving my mother food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the priest found out about us, or learned about us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was a human being.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he started helping us.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
